        <num>CCP 4073</num>
        <heading>4073. Â Functions, duties, and authority of provisional tutor</heading>
        <subsection eId="CCP-4073__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Institute and prosecute an action to enforce judicially a right of the minor; and</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-4073__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Operate a business belonging to the minor.
A provisional tutor shall file an account upon the termination of his authority.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
